{"tid":1643253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（成績表）港鐵連續多日提早收車 酒吧指生意大受打擊","createTime":"2019-10-10T05:00:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T11:11:03.000Z","uid":125168,"like":441,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"a971cd235fa78abea7037704c497c19085a19030","tid":1643253,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:00:09.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】港鐵連續第五日提早收車，入夜後巿面蕭條。酒吧業界指，生意大受打擊，員工上班亦受影響。<br />\n<br />\n晚上八時過後，港鐵站落閘，商場提早結束營業，沙田新城市廣場只有少部分商店在港鐵收車後繼續營業。<br />\n<br />\n平日人來人往的彌敦道，多間商舖提早關門，酒吧只有兩三枱客。<br />\n<br />\n文逸朗是尖沙咀一間樓上酒吧的負責人，他指反修例示威以來，客人都沒有很大意欲消遣，影響生意。<br />\n<br />\n除了賣酒，酒吧亦有提供西餐和串燒，但到七時許客人仍然不多，他說近日港鐵提早收車生意更差。他說不只客人，連員工上班也有影響。<br />\n<br />\n負責人希望社會可以回復平靜，趁十月萬聖節多做優惠，收復失地。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無硝煙嘅戰爭可能先係決勝負嘅關鍵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />下一個check point係無得蒙面嘅萬聖節<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"ef2eefcde36cfddd33f0602d0ac1bfef7bf2c25c","tid":1643253,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:01:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67086eaef5868e656ac876745ce0dd94ebc9c2ed","tid":1643253,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:02:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac08794ae75bde0a0e6d8004a3e6faeb875ac5b4","tid":1643253,"uid":66822,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:02:58.000Z","msg":"星期五中環快閃 撐被捕保安<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FoM1jNJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFoM1jNJ.jpg&h=eaa6b73f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7onWS7K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7onWS7K.jpg&h=4e446c9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d4af556020765a973eaa7e46c74cae05dbfedf9","tid":1643253,"uid":66822,"like":37,"d